   ZURICH
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Lindt &amp; Spruengli, Switzerland's oldest chocolate maker, plans to take over
the troubled Austrian confectioner Hofbauer, Reuter reports from Zurich.
Lindt signed a letter of intent with Hofbauer on May 11 and a definitive
