FT  18 MAY 94 / World Stock Markets: Brazil
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The strong rally on Wall Street and in US bond prices sparked a sharp buying
spree in Brazilian shares, boosting equities in Sao Paulo by 5.5 per cent in
