62m for Mr Steve Morgan, the founder and chief executive, has fallen foul of
the recent fatigue regarding new issues, particularly by housebuilders.
Of the minimum 21.75m shares offered to the public only 17.12m, or 78.7 per
cent, were taken up.
The issue was fully underwritten by Barclays de Zoete Wedd, with Cazenove
acting as broker.
